    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one, and honestly, she looks like she just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been garage-kept, hand-washed every weekend, and the interior still has that 'new car' magic. There might be a tiny, microscopic stone chip if you look with a magnifying glass, but that\u2019s just a sign she\u2019s ready for the open road! I'm only letting her go to a home that'll appreciate her as much as I do. Come by, grab a coffee, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44900.0,
