      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a superlative specimen of engineering, maintained with a level of mechanical sympathy rarely seen outside of private collections. This chassis is laser-straight, exhibiting zero-deflection handling characteristics thanks to a refreshed suspension geometry and meticulous corner-balancing. The high-revving powerplant has been recently compression-tested with factory-spec results across all banks, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency. The gearbox offers surgical precision with crisp, positive engagement through every gate. Cosmetically, the finish remains in a concourse-ready state, showing no signs of high-speed pitting or thermal cycling on the panels. This is a turnkey, investment-grade machine for the driver who demands a visceral, uncompromised experience and understands the value of rigorous preventative maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
